name: Pink Tree Of Life Lava Stone Essential Oil Bracelet
description:
Do you miss your morning routine with your favorite Fuze Body products and wish you could carry them with you throughout the day? With one of these beautiful lava stone bracelets you can. Lava stones are from volcanoes and are like nature's sponge soaking up essential oils so you can enjoy them all day with just 1 - 2 drops and will last from 1 - 7 days
You can also put drops of your own favorite essential oils on the bracelets.
